'''Linda Woolverton''' was the writer for the [[Ewoks (television series)|''Ewoks'']] episodes "[[Baga's Rival]]" and "[[Gone With the Mimphs]]." She is best known as a screenwriter for many of [[The Walt Disney Company|Disney's]] films, including [[Wikipedia:Beauty and the Beast (1991 film)|''Beauty and the Beast'']] and [[Wikipedia:The Lion King|''The Lion King'']].

